      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my ride! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s been incredibly reliable for me. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you. It runs beautifully and is just waiting for a new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
