    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated inline-six mated to a crisp six-speed manual gearbox. This vehicle has been maintained with a focus on longitudinal dynamics and chassis rigidity. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and the installation of poly-bushed control arms to sharpen turn-in response. The limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load, ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved road car, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a precise shift linkage. Upgraded with a stage-one ECU remap and a lightweight flywheel for improved throttle blipping and rev-matching. A turn-key performance machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
