    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a pride-of-ownership machine. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent multi-point inspection that confirmed the engine and transmission are in top form. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with responsive handling, making it an ideal choice for a buyer who values both performance and peace of mind.",
