    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s super comfortable, runs like a dream, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready for many more miles. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you're going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
